lyrics:
(1) Me tumse pehli baar mila hoon, dil ko chhoo gaya yeh ehsaas.
(2) Aankhon mein chamak, pyaar ka nasha, rangin hai har pal ka saaz.
(3) Baatein hui kuch khaas, dil ki duniya mein hai pyaara saa raaz.
(4) Saath chalte hain hum, yeh safar hai pyaar ka ek aasmaan.
(5) Ho gaya hai dil beqaraar, teri bahaon mein hai sukoon ka jahaan.
(6) Tere saath bitaya har lamha, hai mere dil ka khaas hissa.
(7) Mehfil mein teri muskurahat, ban gayi meri zindagi ka asli maksad.
(8) Baarish ki boondein, sargam ban gayi, teri muskurahat se saari duniya roshan.
